Generic single-database configuration.

## Some commands

- alembic --help
1. alembic init alembic
2. alembic revision -m "create post table"
3. alembic upgrade <revision_no. from the above file>  
4. alembic revision -m "add content column to posts table"
5. alembic current
6. alembic heads
7. alembic upgrade head or alembic upgrade <revision_no. from the above file>  
8. for rollback >>  alembic downgrade <revision_no. from the above file>  or alembic downgrade <int number>
9. alembic revision -m "add foreign-key to posts table"
10. alembic revision --autogenerate -m "auto vote"

